fields.about: Hi, I am Jane Doe, Avid student of life! I love learning new things. What's great about music is that there are always new ways and things. I belive that the best way to learn is to teach. That's why I started actually. Now I teach to help others while I hone my own skills.

I have worked as a freelance Illustrator since 1993. I enjoyed doing a variety of work from being a courtroom sketch artist and animation character development artist, to illustrating corporate annual reports and children's books. I currently have illustrated books that are sold in Barnes and Noble and on Amazon.

Hello, I am Gloria and I teach Photography and styling  classes. I trained as a scientist, worked in Biotech and human vaccines, and after having my first baby, discovered the joys of Instagram and developed a new passion for photography. 7 years later, I now create beautiful imagery for designers and businesses (big and small) and help them advocate for themselves online and on social media.

Throughout her illustrious, decorated career, Mundy "The Guru as refered to by fans and clients alike has resoundingly earned her reputation as one of the most renowned recording and mixing engineers in music today, having worked with artists such as Jay-Z, Beyonce, Rick Ross, Drake, T.I., Kanye West and Eminem.

I am an author, Youtuber, and speaker who is passionate about helping students succeed. Most of my work today is done at College Info Geek - a site I created in 2010 in order to share my experience in becoming a more effective student.
